Dragon Apotheosis	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.DragonDiscipleClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 10th level, a dragon disciple fully realizes his draconic heritage and takes on the half-dragon template (see page 146 of the Monster Manual). His breath weapon reaches full strength (as noted above), and he gains +4 to Strength and +2 to Charisma. His natural armor bonus increases to +4, and he acquires low-light vision, 60-foot darkvision, immunity to sleep and paralysis effects, and immunity to the energy type used by his breath weapon (see above).	KEY:Dragon Disciple ~ Dragon Apotheosis									BONUS:STAT|STR|4	BONUS:STAT|CHA|2	BONUS:VAR|HasLowLightVision|1	BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|60|TYPE=Base						ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Immunity to Sleep|Immunity To Paralysis								SORTKEY:Class_Dragon_Disciple	SOURCEPAGE:DMG	
